quran[30{c,v,t}:
87,16,magar tum log to duniya ki zindagi ko ikhtiyar karte ho
87,17,halaank akhirat bohat behtar aur paindah tar hai
87,18,yeh baat pehlay shifon mein ( marqoom ) hai
87,19,( yani ) ibrahim aur moose ke shifon mein
88,1,bhala tum ko dhaanp lainay wali ( yani qayamat ka ) haal maloom howa hai
88,2,is roz bohat se munh ( walay ) zaleel hon ge
88,3,sakht mehnat karne walay thakey manday
88,4,dehakti aag mein daakhil hon ge
88,5,aik kholtey hue chashmay ka un ko pani pilaya jaye ga
88,6,aur khaar daar jhaad ke siwa un ke liye koi khana nahi ( ho ga )
88,7,jo nah farbahi laaye aur nah bhook mein kuch kaam aeye
88,8,aur bohat se munh ( walay ) is roz shaadmaan hon ge
88,9,apne aamaal ( ki jaza ) se khush dil
88,10,bahisht bareen mein
88,11,wahan kisi terhan ki bakwaas nahi sunen ge
88,12,is mein chashmay bah rahay hon ge
88,13,wahan takhat hon ge ounchay bichay hue
88,14,aur aabkhoray ( qareene se ) rakhay hue
88,15,aur gayo takiye qitaar ki qitaar lagey hue
88,16,aur nafees musannaden bichi hui
88,17,yeh log oonton ki taraf nahi dekhte ke kaisay ( ajeeb ) peda kiye gay hain
88,18,aur aasman ki taraf ke kaisa bulandkiya gaya hai
88,19,aur pahoron ki taraf ke kis terhan kharray kiye gay hain
88,20,aur zameen ki taraf ke kis terhan bichai gayi
88,21,to tum nasiyaat karte raho ke tum nasiyaat karne walay hi ho
88,22,tum un par Darogha nahi ho
88,23,haan jis ne munh phera aur nah maana
88,24,to khuda is ko bara azaab day ga
88,25,be shak un ko hamaray paas lout kar aana hai
88,26,phir hum hi ko un se hisaab lena hai
